body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for reaching out to Car Solutions. My name is Austin Evans. May I have your name please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Shirley. Could you provide me your phone number for account verification purposes, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's eight six seven five five five zero nine.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great, thank you. Could you also confirm your date of birth, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Yes, it's zero three one two one nine seven eight.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Shirley, for providing that information. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for contacting us today, Shirley. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
